title: Deuces Wild: A 222 MPH Lap Around Daytona International Speedway
description: Colin Braun took a 3.5L V6 EcoBoost engine 222 MPH around Daytona International Speedway inside a Michael Shank Racing Daytona Prototype. Hang on. It's faster than any man has ever driven around Daytona.
